{"id":1132529435,"question_id":3031,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"5 months, 4 weeks","timestamp":1703975455,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"32 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1132529435/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Construct Product Matrix","memory":"72.4 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    final long MOD = 12345;\n    public int[][] constructProductMatrix(int[][] grid) {\n        int n = grid.length;\n        int m = grid[0].length;\n        int[][] res = new int[n][m];\n        long pre = 1, suf = 1;\n        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n            for (int j = 0; j < m; j++) {\n                res[i][j] = (int)(pre);\n                pre = pre * grid[i][j] % MOD;\n            }\n        }\n\n        for (int i = n-1; i >=0; i--) {\n            for (int j = m-1; j >= 0; j--) {\n                res[i][j] = (int)(suf * res[i][j] % MOD);\n                suf = suf * grid[i][j] % MOD;\n            }\n        }\n\n        return res;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"construct-product-matrix","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
